CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: The Generation Essentials Group, jointly established by AMTD Group, AMTD IDEA Group and AMTD Digital Inc., is headquartered in France and focuses on global strategies and developments in multi-media, entertainment, and cultural affairs worldwide as well as hospitality and VIP services. TGE comprises L'Officiel, The Art Newspaper, movie and entertainment projects. Collectively, TGE is a diversified portfolio of media and entertainment businesses, and a global portfolio of premium properties.
